<D>__{you have a boss that has a laryngectomy?}
<C>__{colin}
<D>__{no, no, no. that was a guy who works for me.}
<C>__{madolyn}
<D>__{you're lying to me.}
<C>__{colin}
<D>__{not exactly.}
<P>__{(the charming colin:)}
<D>__{there are certain things i will not be able to talk to you about. i cannot allow you to jeopardize an ongoing investigation. (or your}
<P>__{own life.) (more seriously, after a long beat)}
<D>__{there really are things connected to my job that you can't ask about. that you don't want to know about.}
<C>__{madolyn}
